{"tid":812552,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"突然覺得好頹好空虛","createTime":"2018-09-09T17:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T18:21:28.000Z","uid":203262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c57f1b8b0429bbdb30d29e750d63cd1e9fc53e6c","tid":812552,"uid":203262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"自問係一個好鐘意笑 玩起上嚟癲癲地嘅人<br />\n以前中學日日翻學嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n從來未試過覺得空虛甚至頹<br />\n畢業之後呢種感覺開始湧現直到依家愈嚟愈頻密<br />\n原因不明 無話有咩事發生令到我咁<br />\n雖則話就話瞓醒之後又係一條好漢<br />\n但係呢種感覺出現嘅時候真係好難受<br />\n難受到我有時會默默流馬尿<br />\n有懷疑過自己係咪有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係其實人大咗個個都會咁"},{"pid":"e0ef0c71aeebe30571a0472219bbf7466205bac0","tid":812552,"uid":207426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db3aa2bd3c3ce873da2f9ca7b70750336ab87164","tid":812552,"uid":203262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ef0c71aeebe30571a0472219bbf7466205bac0","tid":812552,"uid":207426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:21:28.000Z","msg":"好想留喺中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔想面對社會"}]}